1.under the node folder create a new folder called ass ticket-master-bk
2.setup, install and configure express
3.create 2 schemas
   1 - Customer
     - name
     - email
     - mobile
 
   2 - Department
     - name

   3 - Employee      procrastination
     - name
     - email
     - mobile

    4 create routes
      GET/customers - list all customers
      GET/departments - list all departments
      GET/employees - list all employees


      POST/customers - create a customer - name, email, mobile
      POST/departments - create a department - name
      POST/employees - create a employee - name, email, mobile
      
       